Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.74,0:00:45.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当且仅当两端的分子\N{\fs36}If, and only if, both sides of the numerator is divisible by
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.70,0:00:49.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都能被这两个未知变量的平方根的倒数整除时\N{\fs36}the inverse of the square root of the two unassigned variables.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.76,0:00:53.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 除了当X轴上的坐标值\N{\fs36}Good. Except when the value of the "X" Coordinate...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.14,0:00:55.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,小于等于1的时候\N{\fs36}is equal to or less than the value of one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.74,0:00:58.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 怎么了 Isaac  - 那道题怎么了\N{\fs36}- Yes, Isaac? - What about that problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.84,0:01:02.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 那个啊 不用去想那题 "M"是\N{\fs36}Oh, that? Don't worry about that. "M" Is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.66,0:01:04.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 为什么\N{\fs36}Wait. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.76,0:01:05.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就写着玩的\N{\fs36}I just put that up as a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.92,0:01:08.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那大概是全世界最难的几何方程式了\N{\fs36}That's probably the hardest geometry equation in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.33,0:01:11.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解出来能得多少额外学分呢\N{\fs36}How much extra credit is it worth?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.15,0:01:14.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛 鉴于我还没见任何人答对过\N{\fs36}Well, considering I've never seen anyone get it right...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.01,0:01:17.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包括我在麻省理工的导师 Leaky博士\N{\fs36}including my mentor, Dr. Leaky at M.I.T....
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.44,0:01:20.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在座任何一位能解答出来的人\N{\fs36}I guess if anyone here can solve that problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.01,0:01:21.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我敢肯定 \N{\fs36}I'd see to it that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.84,0:01:25.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,余生都不需要再学数学了\N{\fs36}none of you ever have to open another math book again for the rest of your lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.96,0:01:34.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Max\N{\fs36}Max?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.61,0:01:36.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想试试吗\N{\fs36}Care to try it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.42,0:01:40.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 是有人叫了我的名字吗\N{\fs36}I'm sorry. Did someone say my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.25,0:02:20.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你解出来了\N{\fs36}You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.89,0:02:28.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fischer Fischer Fischer Fischer Fischer\N{\fs36}Fischer! Fischer! Fischer! Fischer! Fischer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.48,0:02:43.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs36}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:47.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们拥有的一切都来得轻而易举\N{\fs36}You guys have it real easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.88,0:02:51.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不曾拥有这样的成长环境\N{\fs36}I never had it like this where I grew up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.89,0:02:55.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我把我的孩子送到这里\N{\fs36}But I send my kids here because, the fact is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.25,0:02:58.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这里是全国最好的学校之一\N{\fs36}you go to one of the best schools in the country:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.62,0:02:59.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉什莫尔\N{\fs36}Rushmore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.33,0:03:01.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于你们中的某些人来说\N{\fs36}Now, for some of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.46,0:03:03.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这并不重要\N{\fs36}it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.22,0:03:08.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们含着金汤匙出生 将世代富有\N{\fs36}You were born rich, and you're going to stay rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.93,0:03:11.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但对于另外一部分人 我的建议是\N{\fs36}But here's my advice to the rest of you:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.12,0:03:16.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死死瞄准这些富家少爷\N{\fs36}Take dead aim on the rich boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.32,0:03:19.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盯着准星里的每个人\N{\fs36}Get them in the crosshairs,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.90,0:03:21.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿下他们\N{\fs36}and take them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.36,0:03:23.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记住\N{\fs36}Just remember:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.10,0:03:29.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们虽然在物质上富有一切 但永远买不到骨气\N{\fs36}They can buy anything, but they can't buy backbone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.79,0:03:31.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时刻提醒他们这一点\N{\fs36}Don't let them forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.84,0:03:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs36}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.68,0:03:44.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有空来毕业典礼吗 Herman 你可以做个返场演讲\N{\fs36}Free for graduation, Herman? Perhaps you could give us an encore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.30,0:03:46.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Nicholas Copernicus  - 我才不在乎\N{\fs36}- Nicholas! Copernicus! - I don't give a shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.80,0:03:48.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老子出钱建了整个游泳馆\N{\fs36}I paid for the whole damn natatorium.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.62,0:03:50.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这帮小崽子至少得听我把话说完吧\N{\fs36}The least these little pricks can do is hear me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.60,0:03:53.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 您好 Guggenheim教授  - 你好 Max\N{\fs36}- Hi, Dr. Guggenheim. - Hello, Max.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.98,0:03:55.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您好 我是Max Fischer\N{\fs36}Hello. I'm Max Fischer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.29,0:03:59.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想跟您说 我非常赞同您对拉什莫尔的观点\N{\fs36}I just wanted to say that I strongly agree with your views concerning Rushmore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.69,0:04:02.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 您的演讲非常精彩\N{\fs36}Um... your speech was excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.56,0:04:05.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 谢谢  - 谢谢您\N{\fs36}- Thank you. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.62,0:04:07.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 谢谢  - 您好\N{\fs36}- Thank you. - Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.16,0:04:10.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 Blume先生 他是我的教友 Dirk Calloway\N{\fs36}Oh, Mr. Blume, this is my chapel partner, Dirk Calloway.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.16,0:04:10.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs38}教友 学院中高年级学生和低年级学生组成的\N一同进行祷告颂诗的伙伴关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.75,0:04:13.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸会 Dirk\N{\fs36}Nice to meet you, Dirk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.17,0:04:14.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs36}Well, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.45,0:04:20.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个\N{\fs36}You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.76,0:04:24.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得关于拉什莫尔您讲的太对了\N{\fs36}I really think you're right about Rushmore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.32,0:04:26.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 Drik\N{\fs36}Come on, Dirk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.68,0:04:32.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 他叫什么来着  - Max Fischer\N{\fs36}- What's his name again? - Max Fischer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.73,0:04:34.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很机灵的小鬼\N{\fs36}Sharp little guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.32,0:04:40.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是我们这儿最麻烦的学生之一\N{\fs36}He's one of the worst students we've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.80,0:05:29.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 出局\N{\fs36}You! You're out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.69,0:06:01.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们将把你列入"紧急留校察看"名单\N{\fs36}We're putting you on what we call "Sudden death academic probation."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.53,0:06:03.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么意思呢\N{\fs36}And what does that entail?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.68,0:06:08.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意思就是 要是你再挂一门课 就会被勒令退学\N{\fs36}It entails that if you fail another class you'll be asked to leave Rushmore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.61,0:06:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换句话说 就是我会被开除\N{\fs36}In other words, I'll be expelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.28,0:06:12.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说对了\N{\fs36}That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.74,0:06:14.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能看看相关的文字档案吗\N{\fs36}Could I see some documentation on that, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.13,0:06:20.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社团活动太多 学习时间太少\N{\fs36}Too many extracurricular activities, Max. Not enough studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.04,0:06:22.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fs36}Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.50,0:06:28.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Guggenheim教授 不是我对您的工作指手画脚\N{\fs36}Dr. Guggenheim, I don't want to tell you how to do your job...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.08,0:06:32.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但事实是 无论我多努力学习 还是很可能再挂掉一门课\N{\fs36}but the fact is, no matter how hard I try I still might flunk another class.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.39,0:06:36.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那意味着留级一年 悉听尊便\N{\fs36}If that means I have to stay on for a postgraduate year, then so be it,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.76,0:06:38.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 但是  - 我们并没有留级制度\N{\fs36}- But... - We don't offer a postgraduate year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.38,0:06:42.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是此前没有而已\N{\fs36}Well... we don't offer it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.36,0:06:44.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,努把力提高成绩吧\N{\fs36}Just bring up the grades.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.23,0:06:47.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您还记得我是怎么进入这所学校的吗\N{\fs36}Do you remember how I got into this school?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.29,0:06:50.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得 你写了一出话剧\N{\fs36}Yes. You wrote a play.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.56,0:06:53.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 二年级的时候\N{\fs36}That's right. Second grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.82,0:06:56.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我写了一出关于"水门事件"的独幕剧\N{\fs36}A little one-act about Watergate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.82,0:06:56.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs38}水门事件 1972年总统大选中尼克松的竞选团队\N在水门大厦安装窃听器并偷拍机密文件时当场被捕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.78,0:06:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我妈妈看了之后觉得我应该去拉什莫尔读书\N{\fs36}And my mother read it and felt I should go to Rushmore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.28,0:07:01.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后您读了剧本 还给了我奖学金 不是吗\N{\fs36}And you read it, and you gave me a scholarship, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.85,0:07:03.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs36}Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.73,0:07:07.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 您后悔吗  - 不 我不后悔\N{\fs36}- Do you regret it? - No, I don't regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.67,0:07:09.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我仍然可能不得不开除你\N{\fs36}But I still might have to expel you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.49,0:07:14.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不可以 可不可以睁一只眼闭一只眼呢\N{\fs36}Couldn't Couldn't we just let me float by?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.53,0:07:17.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看在往日的情分上\N{\fs36}For old time's sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.25,0:07:18.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以 Max\N{\fs36}Can't do it, Max.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.89,0:07:23.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 他们想踢我出去  - 不是吧 又来\N{\fs36}- They want to kick me out. - Oh, no. Not again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.98,0:07:26.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你打算怎么办  - 我想我唯一能做的\N{\fs36}- What are you gonna do? - The only thing I can do:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.61,0:07:29.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是争取抱上教务处的大腿\N{\fs36}try and pull some strings with the administration, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.37,0:07:36.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听说了下学期要开日语课吗\N{\fs36}Did you hear they're teaching Japanese next year?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.49,0:07:38.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是传闻而已\N{\fs36}That's the rumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.12,0:07:41.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 还要取消拉丁语课  - 什么\N{\fs36}- And they're canceling Latin. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.67,0:07:45.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为了取消拉丁语课摇旗呐喊了5年\N{\fs36}I tried to get Latin canceled for five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.63,0:07:47.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"这是一门死去的语言" 我一直这样说\N{\fs36}"It's a dead language," I'd always say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.88,0:07:50.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜他们总算听到了你的心声吧\N{\fs36}Well, I guess they finally heard you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.14,0:08:07.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失陪一下\N{\fs36}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.57,0:08:10.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不可以看一下\N{\fs36}Could I please see a list of all the people
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.24,0:08:12.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去年借阅这本书的人的名单\N{\fs36}who've checked out this book in the past year?
