Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.14,0:09:43.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天我还跟Calloway先生说\N{\fs36}I was just telling Mr.Calloway the other day
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.88,0:09:46.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有你关照Drik 我们真的很省心\N{\fs36}how fortunate we are to have someone like you looking out for Dirk.
