Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.34,0:10:35.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫那个苏格兰大猩猩闭上不干不净的臭嘴\N{\fs36}Just tell that deformed Scottish gorilla to shut his fat face.
