Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.10,0:10:44.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你谁啊 律师么\N{\fs36}What are you, a lawyer?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.98,0:10:46.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您好 Blume先生\N{\fs36}Hey, Mr. Blume.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.76,0:10:48.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您好 我是Max Fischer\N{\fs36}Hey. It's Max Fischer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.96,0:10:50.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 你好\N{\fs36}Oh, hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.44,0:10:51.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 Max 我妈来了\N{\fs36}Hey, Max. My mom just showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.82,0:10:53.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早点走可以吗 完毕\N{\fs36}Is it okay if I leave early? Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.86,0:10:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然可以 Charlie\N{\fs36}Sure, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.41,0:11:03.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的秘诀是什么 Max\N{\fs36}What's the secret, Max?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.66,0:11:04.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么秘诀\N{\fs36}"The secret"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.86,0:11:08.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是 你好像看透一切的样子\N{\fs36}Yeah. Well, you seem to have it pretty figured out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.88,0:11:10.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个啊 我也不知道\N{\fs36}The secret. I don't know. Uh
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.68,0:11:14.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得你只需要找到自己想做的事情\N{\fs36}I think you just gotta find something you love to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.14,0:11:15.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后终身为之努力就可以了\N{\fs36}and then do it for the rest of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.42,0:11:18.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说 这件事就是进拉什莫尔\N{\fs36}For me, it's going to Rushmore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.08,0:11:24.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 前排归我  - 嘿 Ronny 嘿 Donny 你们好啊\N{\fs36}- Shotgun. - Hey, Ronny. Hey, Donny. How you guys
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.12,0:11:27.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 滚到后面去 我说了"前排归我"  - 你就坐后面吧 Donny\N{\fs36}- Get in the back. I said "Shotgun." - Get in the back, Donny.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.58,0:11:31.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开车吧\N{\fs36}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.77,0:11:38.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你们邀请那孩子参加生日聚会了吗  - Max Fischer吗\N{\fs36}- Did you invite that kid to your party? - Max Fischer?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.20,0:11:40.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉倒吧老爸 会有女孩子在那儿的 我才不会叫他来\N{\fs36}Come on, Dad. There's gonna be girls there. I'd rather die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.40,0:11:42.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脑子糊涂了老头\N{\fs36}Pull your head out of your ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.38,0:11:47.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 晚安 Littlejeans先生  - 晚安 Max\N{\fs36}- Good night, Mr. Littlejeans. - Good night, Max.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.29,0:11:48.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天见\N{\fs36}I'll see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.13,0:11:58.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能看看后面吗\N{\fs36}May I see the back, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.17,0:12:00.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然可以\N{\fs36}Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.12,0:12:06.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得怎么样\N{\fs36}How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.28,0:12:07.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs36}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.45,0:12:12.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺便说一下 几何试卷上要签个字\N{\fs36}I need a signature on this geometry test, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.38,0:12:14.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我瞧瞧\N{\fs36}Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.44,0:12:19.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 嗯  - 我知道 我知道\N{\fs36}- Hmm. - I know, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.90,0:12:20.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,37分\N{\fs36}A 37.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.49,0:12:25.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 我不知道该怎么办了\N{\fs36}Oh, I don't know what to do anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.74,0:12:29.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来可能更糟的\N{\fs36}It could have been worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.75,0:12:32.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你差一点就能得A了\N{\fs36}You almost got the "A."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.79,0:12:35.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么差点能得A 爸 你写什么呢\N{\fs36}"Almost got the 'A"'? Dad, what are you writing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.63,0:12:46.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是我花太多时间在创立社团还有话剧上了\N{\fs36}Maybe I'm spending too much of my time starting up clubs and putting on plays.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.97,0:12:49.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有可能\N{\fs36}That's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.10,0:12:52.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许我应该更努力去泡妞\N{\fs36}I should probably be trying harder to score chicks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.85,0:12:56.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那才是大家真正在意的唯一一件事\N{\fs36}That's the only thing anybody really cares about.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.15,0:12:59.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惜我并不擅长\N{\fs36}It's not my forte, unfortunately.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.48,0:13:01.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生活就是这样 Max\N{\fs36}It'll happen, Max.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.86,0:13:04.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就像那些快帆船的船长\N{\fs36}It's just You're like one of those clipper ship captains.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.78,0:13:06.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大海是你的宿命\N{\fs36}You're married to the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.95,0:13:08.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 没错\N{\fs36}Yes, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.95,0:13:11.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我在海上漂流的太久了\N{\fs36}But I've been out to sea for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.54,0:13:20.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fs36}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.30,0:13:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fs36}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.81,0:13:32.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢你的帽子\N{\fs36}I like your hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.81,0:13:35.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 谢谢\N{\fs36}Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.39,0:13:37.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是这儿的老师 是吧\N{\fs36}You're a teacher here, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.15,0:13:42.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜这是你来拉什莫尔的第一年\N{\fs36}And this is your first year at Rushmore, I take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.40,0:13:43.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs36}Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.24,0:13:48.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不介意的话我想问 你抽烟多久了\N{\fs36}And how long have you been a smoker, if you don't mind me asking?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.28,0:13:49.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想想\N{\fs36}Well, let's see now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.08,0:13:53.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你多大了  - 十五\N{\fs36}- H-How old are you? - Fifteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.54,0:13:56.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我在你这个年纪就开始抽了  - 不是吧\N{\fs36}- Since I was your age. - You're kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.50,0:13:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你该戒烟了\N{\fs36}You should quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.42,0:14:00.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说得对\N{\fs36}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.67,0:14:03.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也该少管闲事了\N{\fs36}And I should mind my own business.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.36,0:14:12.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺便问一句 你在哪念的大学啊\N{\fs36}Where did you go to school, by the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.80,0:14:14.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 哈佛  - 真的吗\N{\fs36}- Harvard. - Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.97,0:14:16.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是巧了\N{\fs36}That's a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:19.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最想申请的两个学校就是牛津和索邦\N{\fs36}My top schools where I want to apply to are Oxford and the Sorbonne.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.36,0:14:21.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈佛保底\N{\fs36}My safety's Harvard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.69,0:14:24.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 很有野心嘛  - 谢谢夸奖\N{\fs36}- That's very ambitious. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.06,0:14:26.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想学什么专业\N{\fs36}What do you want to study?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.14,0:14:31.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛 我还没完全定下来\N{\fs36}Well... I haven't decided for sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.07,0:14:35.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过应该是主修数学和医学双学位\N{\fs36}but probably a double major in mathematics and premed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.70,0:14:37.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你主修的是什么\N{\fs36}What was your major?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.79,0:14:39.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有主修学科\N{\fs36}I didn't have a major,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.50,0:14:42.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我的毕业论文是关于拉丁美洲的经济政策\N{\fs36}But my thesis was on Latin American economic policy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.75,0:14:44.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 挺有意思的\N{\fs36}Oh, that's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.06,0:14:46.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听说下学期不教拉丁语了吗\N{\fs36}Did you hear they're not going to teach Latin here anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.22,0:14:49.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这儿更像是中美洲国家\N{\fs36}This was more like Central America.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.80,0:14:52.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 中美国家之类的 嗯\N{\fs36}Oh, Central America and whatnot. Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.01,0:14:55.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续之前的话题 下学期不教拉丁语了\N{\fs36}But moving on: They're gonna cancel Latin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.96,0:14:58.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学院打算新开一门日语课\N{\fs36}They've got to make room for Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.14,0:15:02.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太遗憾了 因为整个罗曼斯语系都是以拉丁语为基础的\N{\fs36}That's a shame because all the Romance languages are based on Latin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.31,0:15:05.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 是这样的 不是吗\N{\fs36}Yeah, they are, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.73,0:15:07.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nihilo sanctum estne\N{\fs36}Nihilo sanctum estne?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.32,0:15:10.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思\N{\fs36}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.28,0:15:13.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 是拉丁语吧 什么意思啊\N{\fs36}Oh, it's Latin, isn't it? What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.83,0:15:16.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有什么是神圣的了吗\N{\fs36}Is nothing sacred?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.00,0:15:26.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sic transit gloria\N{\fs36}Sic transit gloria.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.17,0:15:27.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,荣光已逝\N{\fs36}Glory fades.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.71,0:15:29.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫Max Fischer.\N{\fs36}I'm Max Fischer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.34,0:15:32.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你好  - 你好\N{\fs36}- Hi. - Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.70,0:15:40.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 快 快 快签  - 麻烦签这里\N{\fs36}- Come on, come on. File out. - Sign here, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.35,0:15:42.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 荣光已逝  - 好 很好\N{\fs36}- Sic transit gloria. - All right, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.15,0:15:52.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后 我就一个问题\N{\fs36}In summation, I have only one question:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.22,0:15:55.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉丁语已死吗\N{\fs36}Is Latin dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.71,0:16:04.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么不去死 Fischer 你个低能废物\N{\fs36}Why don't you just piss off, Fischer, you dotty wee skid mark?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.32,0:16:05.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那句是拉丁语么\N{\fs36}Was that Latin?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.13,0:16:18.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么也没想过 自己会生出这样的儿子\N{\fs36}Never in my wildest imagination did I ever dream I would have sons like these.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.50,0:16:22.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你爸爸是做什么工作的 Max\N{\fs36}What's your dad do, Max?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.02,0:16:27.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是圣约瑟夫医院的一名神经外科医生\N{\fs36}He's a neurosurgeon at, uh, St. Joseph's Hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:31.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就我个人而言 我永远做不到剖开某个人的脑袋\N{\fs36}Personally, I could never see myself cutting open somebody's brain,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.82,0:16:33.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我爸看上去很享受\N{\fs36}but he seems to enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.89,0:16:37.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 不用不用 我来付\N{\fs36}Oh, no, no, no. I got this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.25,0:16:42.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没记错的话 您参加过越南战争是吗\N{\fs36}So you were in Vietnam, if I'm not mistaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.46,0:16:43.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs36}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.45,0:16:46.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,境遇很糟吗\N{\fs36}Were you in the shit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.24,0:16:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 很糟\N{\fs36}Yeah, I was in the shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.20,0:16:52.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周日见 Blume先生\N{\fs36}See you Sunday, Mr. Blume.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.48,0:16:53.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs36}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.65,0:16:54.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周日有什么事吗\N{\fs36}What's on Sunday?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.69,0:16:57.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 想起来了 是双胞胎的生日聚会\N{\fs36}Oh, that's right. The twins' birthday party.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.65,0:17:01.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想来吗\N{\fs36}Do you want to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.56,0:17:05.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很想去 但我已经有约了\N{\fs36}I'd love to, except I've already got a previous obligation to attend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.57,0:17:07.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过还是谢谢您的邀请\N{\fs36}Yeah. Thanks for the invitation though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.89,0:17:12.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来给我做事吧\N{\fs36}Come work for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.61,0:17:17.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 什么意思  - 意思就是 我 我能用上你这样的人\N{\fs36}- What do you mean? - I mean, I-I-I could use someone like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.78,0:17:22.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可能不是什么有钱人 Blume先生\N{\fs36}Look, I may not be rich, Mr. Blume.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.33,0:17:24.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爸可能也只是个医生 但我们应付得来\N{\fs36}My father may only be a doctor, but we manage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.09,0:17:26.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,112号\N{\fs36}One-twelves!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:28.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失陪了 Blume先生 跟您聊天很愉快\N{\fs36}Excuse me, Mr. Blume. Nice talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.26,0:17:32.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也参加了摔角队吗\N{\fs36}You're on the team?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.72,0:17:34.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是替补\N{\fs36}I'm an alternate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.43,0:17:38.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近怎么样 很高兴再次见到你\N{\fs36}How you doin'? Good to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.05,0:17:50.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 酷毙了\N{\fs36}Whoa. Neat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.22,0:19:11.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cross小姐\N{\fs36}Miss Cross?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.50,0:19:15.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我应该让你知道 根据我们那天的对话\N{\fs36}I thought I'd just let you know as per our conversation the other day
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.46,0:19:17.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 拉丁语吗  - 是的 罗曼斯语系\N{\fs36}- Latin? - Right. The Romance languages.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.34,0:19:20.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我做了一个小型演讲  - 我听说了\N{\fs36}- Well, I gave a little speech. - I heard about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.07,0:19:21.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛\N{\fs36}Oh, you did?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.66,0:19:25.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你说服了大家\N{\fs36}I understand you made a very convincing argument.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.66,0:19:31.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是觉得你听到这个消息会很高兴\N{\fs36}I just thought you'd be pleased to hear they're gonna continue the Latin program.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.21,0:19:33.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实让我印象深刻\N{\fs36}I'm very impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.92,0:19:35.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很感谢你\N{\fs36}Well, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.64,0:19:39.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 您需要助手吗\N{\fs36}Hey, you need an assistant?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.85,0:19:41.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里可以雇用助手吗\N{\fs36}Do we get to have an assistant around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.72,0:19:43.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该不行吧\N{\fs36}No, I doubt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.43,0:19:47.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是拿奖学金的 学术奖学金 所以得做一些奇怪的工作\N{\fs36}I'm on scholarship though academic scholarship so I get to do odd jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.72,0:19:51.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是怎么决定到拉什莫尔来教书的呢\N{\fs36}And Say, how did you decide to teach at Rushmore?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.19,0:19:52.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我丈夫先来了这里\N{\fs36}My husband went here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.65,0:19:59.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我不知道你结婚了\N{\fs36}I, uh I didn't know you were married.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.11,0:20:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他已经去世了\N{\fs36}Well, he's dead now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.04,0:20:03.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以事实上我也不算已婚了\N{\fs36}So I'm not, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.20,0:20:05.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他什么时候去世的\N{\fs36}When did he die?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.62,0:20:07.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去年\N{\fs36}Last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.06,0:20:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我妈妈也去世了\N{\fs36}My mother's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.98,0:20:14.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很抱歉\N{\fs36}I'm sorry to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.24,0:20:16.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我7岁那年她就去世了\N{\fs36}She died when I was seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.13,0:20:20.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我们家里都有人过世了\N{\fs36}I guess we both have dead people in our families.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.64,0:20:27.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是怎么回事\N{\fs36}What's going on in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.41,0:20:32.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些小鱼是刚出生的\N{\fs36}These were just born.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.85,0:20:37.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要合金 我要钢材\N{\fs36}I don't want alloys. I want steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.69,0:20:40.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说什么我才不管\N{\fs36}I don't give a rat's ass what he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.16,0:20:46.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要钢材 Harry\N{\fs36}Steel, Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.78,0:20:49.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以你改主意要来工作了\N{\fs36}So you change your mind and you want the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.52,0:20:52.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 但我有个主意 也需要一些资金\N{\fs36}No. But I've got an idea, and I need some money.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.08,0:20:55.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉什莫尔需要的是个水族馆\N{\fs36}What Rushmore needs is an aquarium
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.25,0:20:57.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,设备一流的水族馆 科学家可以在里面演讲\N{\fs36}a first-class aquarium - where the scientists can lecture...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.78,0:20:58.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学生也能在自然生态里\N{\fs36}and the students can observe
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.02,0:21:01.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,观察海洋动物的生活习性\N{\fs36}the marine life in its natural habitat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.18,0:21:02.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道 你觉得呢 Ernie\N{\fs36}I don't know. What do you think, Ernie?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.80,0:21:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个水族馆 养什么鱼\N{\fs36}An aquarium? What kind of fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.80,0:21:07.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梭鱼 魔鬼鱼 电鳗 鳟鱼\N{\fs36}Barracudas, stingrays, electric eel, trout...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.68,0:21:10.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锤头鲨 食人鱼 大乌贼 章\N{\fs36}hammerheads, piranha, giant squid, octopi -
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.60,0:21:12.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,食人鱼 当真吗\N{\fs36}Piranhas? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.18,0:21:14.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 我在跟一个南美洲的人接洽了\N{\fs36}Yes, I'm talking to a guy in South America.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.64,0:21:16.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Guggenheim怎么说  - 什么也没说\N{\fs36}- What'd Guggenheim say? - Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.63,0:21:18.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得我应该先跟你讲\N{\fs36}I felt I should go to you first.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.52,0:21:20.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fs36}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.57,0:21:21.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为在这个阶段\N{\fs36}Because at this moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.86,0:21:24.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得先低调行事为好\N{\fs36}I feel the best strategy is to keep it low profile.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.49,0:21:26.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事前的准备越充分\N{\fs36}The more preparation work I can do...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.22,0:21:27.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟教务处提议的时候\N{\fs36}the stronger our case will be
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.34,0:21:29.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,方案就越有说服力\N{\fs36}when we take it to the administration.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.03,0:21:30.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想要多少资金\N{\fs36}How much money do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.95,0:21:34.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就初步计划而言 三万五千美金 \N{\fs36}$35,000, for the initial plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.26,0:21:45.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给你两千五\N{\fs36}I'll give you 2,500.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.72,0:21:47.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs36}Okay.
