Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.35,0:22:36.27,歌词,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1270,12)\fad(100,100)}*放出的璀璨光芒*\N{\fs35\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI Light\b1}*In the starry sky*
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.35,0:22:38.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 谢谢  - 不客气\N{\fs36}- Thank you. - You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.02,0:23:18.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Max  - 怎么了\N{\fs36}- Max? - Mm-hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.60,0:23:21.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我可以问你个问题吗  - 当然\N{\fs36}- Can I ask you something? - Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.98,0:23:26.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有没想过 你对我来说可能太小了\N{\fs36}Has it ever crossed your mind that you're far too young for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.99,0:23:33.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我确实想过\N{\fs36}It crossed my mind that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.12,0:23:35.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 年龄问题可能会成为你的顾虑之一  - 是\N{\fs36}- you might consider that a possibility. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.37,0:23:38.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更不用说你还是个学生\N{\fs36}Quite apart from the fact that you're a student
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.16,0:23:41.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不想逼你做任何事 Cross小姐\N{\fs36}I'm not trying to pressure you into anything, Miss Cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.33,0:23:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很惊讶你这么直接地提出这件事\N{\fs36}I'm surprised you brought it up so bluntly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.63,0:23:45.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想确认一下\N{\fs36}I just want to make sure -
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.84,0:23:50.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我们已经是好朋友了 对吗  - 对\N{\fs36}- We've become friends, haven't we? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.80,0:23:52.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fs36}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.80,0:23:54.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 呃\N{\fs36}And, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.30,0:23:58.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实是 我们都不清楚\N{\fs36}the - the truth is neither one of us has the slightest idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.68,0:24:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这段关系会怎么发展\N{\fs36}where this relationship is going.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.52,0:24:02.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不可能预测未来\N{\fs36}We can't predict the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.31,0:24:04.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们没有关系 Max\N{\fs36}We don't have a relationship, Max.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.44,0:24:07.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 但我们是朋友  - 是的 我们只能是朋友\N{\fs36}- But we're friends. - Yes, and that's all we're going to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.36,0:24:09.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我说的"关系"呀\N{\fs36}That's all I meant by "Relationship."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.03,0:24:12.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我给你拿本字典吗\N{\fs36}You want me to grab a dictionary?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.11,0:24:15.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我只是想确保彼此明白对方的想法\N{\fs36}No. I just want to make sure that we understand each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.66,0:24:17.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂了\N{\fs36}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.87,0:24:19.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不够吸引你\N{\fs36}You're not attracted to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.96,0:24:23.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生活就是这样\N{\fs36}C'est la vie.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.83,0:24:25.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Max 你才十五岁\N{\fs36}Max, you're 15 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.79,0:24:28.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没到谈吸引力的年纪\N{\fs36}Attraction doesn't enter into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.67,0:24:30.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么就什么吧\N{\fs36}If you say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.98,0:24:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想说的是\N{\fs36}Look, all I'm getting at is that -
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.93,0:24:38.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从来没有遇到过像你这样的人\N{\fs36}that I've never met anyone like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.31,0:24:43.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你想怎样看待它的意义都可以\N{\fs36}So you can take that for whatever it's worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.40,0:24:49.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也从来没遇到过像你这样的人\N{\fs36}I think I can safely say I've never met anyone like you either.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.57,0:24:56.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有吗 \N{\fs36}You haven't, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.33,0:25:01.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要握个手\N{\fs36}Want to shake hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.41,0:25:04.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很高兴我们有这次谈话\N{\fs36}I'm glad we had this conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.42,0:25:07.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是\N{\fs36}So am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.54,0:25:10.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能装窃听器 他们每天都会搜我的身\N{\fs36}I can't wear a wire. They're feeling me up every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.88,0:25:13.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 Frank 你会受到全方位保护的\N{\fs36}Oh, come on, Frank. You'll have complete protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.63,0:25:15.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 这话我之前也听过\N{\fs36}Yeah, I've heard that one before.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.47,0:25:17.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我要去给计时收费表里投一枚硬币  - 坐下 Frank\N{\fs36}- I gotta put a dime in the meter. - Sit down, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.89,0:25:21.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Joe 帮Serpico警官给计时表里投个硬币\N{\fs36}Joe, go put a dime in the meter for Officer Serpico.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.47,0:25:23.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着 Serpico 如果你愿意在法庭上作证\N{\fs36}Look, Serpico, if you agree to testify in open court -
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.06,0:25:25.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 不  - 不什么\N{\fs36}- No! - No, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.02,0:25:27.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我不会作证的\N{\fs36}No, I'm not gonna testify.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.90,0:25:29.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走走走\N{\fs36}Go, go, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.94,0:25:32.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就要上交你的手枪和警徽\N{\fs36}I'll expect your gun and your badge on my desk -
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.49,0:25:36.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 答应我一件事 O'Reilly  - 说\N{\fs36}- Promise me one thing, O'Reilly. - Name it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.61,0:25:38.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要从头到尾一直负责\N{\fs36}That you're gonna follow this thing all the way to the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.95,0:25:41.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这条线\N{\fs36}of the line... where I got to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.70,0:25:43.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就帮点忙吧\N{\fs36}So help me God.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.54,0:25:45.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 有人从那栋楼里出来了  - 有消息\N{\fs36}- Someone coming out of the building. - I've got something!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.87,0:25:48.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 等等 这可能就是他  - 街对面有动静\N{\fs36}- Wait. This could be it. - There's action across the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.79,0:25:50.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 就是他  - 是雪人\N{\fs36}- Yeah, it's him. - It's Snowman.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.42,0:25:55.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 他要上高架火车了  - 抓住他\N{\fs36}- He's getting on the el train! - Take him!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.93,0:26:00.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 奶油卷饼那句怎么回事  - Max\N{\fs36}- What happened to the cannoli line? - Max -
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.22,0:26:01.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该说 "算了 Sanchez\N{\fs36}You're supposed to say, "Forget about it, Sanchez.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.83,0:26:03.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那老家伙爱吃奶油卷饼"\N{\fs36}The old man likes his cannolis."
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.52,0:26:04.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 我是犯了个小错误\N{\fs36}Look, I made a mistake, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.81,0:26:06.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这完全没有影响\N{\fs36}It didn't make any difference anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.31,0:26:08.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没打算继续追究 但别以为这无所谓\N{\fs36}Hey, I'm letting it go, but don't say it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.90,0:26:11.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 所有台词都是字斟句酌的  - 一边去\N{\fs36}- Every line matters. - Get off my back!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.57,0:26:13.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别把我的剧搞砸了\N{\fs36}Don't fuck with my play!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.94,0:26:16.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你这个混蛋  - 喂 分开 快分开\N{\fs36}- You fucking cocksucker - - Hey, break it up. Break it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.15,0:26:17.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要杀了你\N{\fs36}I'm gonna kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.16,0:26:27.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Max Max\N{\fs36}Max. Max.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.48,0:26:54.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得今晚的表演特别优秀\N{\fs36}I thought the acting tonight was excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.69,0:26:57.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 其实它彩排的时候更完美\N{\fs36}Thanks. Well, it was better in rehearsals.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.99,0:27:00.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我晚点再跟你见面 爸 我要赴一个晚餐\N{\fs36}I'll catch up with you later, Dad. I got a dinner to go to.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.78,0:27:04.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 是吗  - 嗯 就跟演员和工作人员\N{\fs36}- Oh, yeah? - Yeah. Cast and crew only.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.12,0:27:06.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 要给你点钱吗  - 不用了 爸  \N{\fs36}- Oh. You need some money? - No, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.62,0:27:13.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 那巴掌怎么样  - 挺好的\N{\fs36}- Well, how was the slap? - It was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.34,0:27:15.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他来了 Max 剧超级棒\N{\fs36}There he is. Max, that was great.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.38,0:27:16.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很高兴你能来\N{\fs36}I'm so glad you could come.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.96,0:27:19.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想让你认识一下我的朋友Peter Flynn 这是Max Fischer\N{\fs36}I want you to meet a friend of mine. Peter Flynn, Max Fischer.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.68,0:27:21.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fs36}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.22,0:27:23.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙是谁\N{\fs36}Who's this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.97,0:27:25.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Peter\N{\fs36}Peter.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.56,0:27:28.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很喜欢你的戏 真的很酷\N{\fs36}I really liked your play. It was really cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.89,0:27:30.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs36}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.27,0:27:33.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的鼻子怎么了\N{\fs36}What happened to your nose?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.15,0:27:35.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我被人揍了一拳  - 噢 天\N{\fs36}- I got punched in the face. - Oh, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.94,0:27:37.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的理由是什么\N{\fs36}What's your excuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.69,0:27:39.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 嗨 大作家  - 你好吗\N{\fs36}- Hey, author. - How you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.93,0:27:41.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 干得漂亮  - 谢谢\N{\fs36}- Nice job. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.46,0:27:43.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚能见到你父亲吗\N{\fs36}Gonna get to meet your dad tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.45,0:27:45.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 他今晚值班\N{\fs36}Oh, no. The old man's on call.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.70,0:27:47.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Blume 我想让你见见Cross小姐\N{\fs36}Mr. Blume, I'd like you to meet Miss Cross -
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.58,0:27:50.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有这位我还不知道名字的先生\N{\fs36}And I didn't catch this young gentleman's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.83,0:27:54.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我挺喜欢你的护士服的\N{\fs36}I like your nurse's uniform, guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.75,0:27:56.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是手术室工作服\N{\fs36}These are O.R. Scrubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.42,0:28:01.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手术室吗\N{\fs36}"O.R." They? -
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.18,0:28:04.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这套衣服和这个餐厅格格不入\N{\fs36}Well, they're totally inappropriate for the occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.09,0:28:06.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不知道我们要出来吃晚餐\N{\fs36}Well, I didn't know we were going to dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.81,0:28:09.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为并没有邀请你\N{\fs36}That's because you weren't invited.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.35,0:28:10.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 Max\N{\fs36}Take it easy, Max.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.52,0:28:12.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你给他点的威士忌和苏打\N{\fs36}You were the one that ordered him a whiskey and soda.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.73,0:28:15.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那有什么错\N{\fs36}So what's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.61,0:28:16.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能写一出好剧\N{\fs36}I can write a hit play.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.79,0:28:19.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么就不能喝点小酒放松一下\N{\fs36}Why can't I have a little drink to unwind myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.86,0:28:24.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我 卷毛 你跟Cross小姐是怎么认识的\N{\fs36}So, tell me, curly, how do you know Miss Cross?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.41,0:28:26.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我们一起在哈佛读书  - 噢 挺好的\N{\fs36}- We went to Harvard together. - Oh, that's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.53,0:28:28.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自编自导了一出很棒的剧\N{\fs36}I wrote a hit play and directed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.62,0:28:31.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我也没落下风\N{\fs36}So I'm not sweating it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.08,0:28:32.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里结账 谢谢\N{\fs36}Can we get a check, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.79,0:28:34.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你以为你在干嘛  - 结账呀\N{\fs36}- What do you think you're doing? - Getting the check.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.96,0:28:36.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用你来 抱歉\N{\fs36}No, you're not. Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.04,0:28:39.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很感谢你为我们调整安排\N{\fs36}I just want to thank you for accommodating us.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.17,0:28:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实原先我们只有三个人\N{\fs36}You see, we only thought we were going to be three...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.42,0:28:44.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但有人不请就自来了 我很抱歉\N{\fs36}but, uh, someone invited himself along, so I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.80,0:28:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 不客气 先生  - 好\N{\fs36}- Quite all right, sir. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.51,0:28:47.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fs36}Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.81,0:28:49.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这样很没礼貌 Max\N{\fs36}You're being rude, Max.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.93,0:28:51.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我没有  - 你就是\N{\fs36}- No, I'm not. - Yes, you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.68,0:28:52.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有 我只是想弄明白\N{\fs36}No, I'm not. I'm just trying to
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.90,0:28:55.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么会带这位先生来看我的剧\N{\fs36}figure out why you brought this gentleman to my play...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.15,0:28:57.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及让他出席这顿没有受邀的晚餐\N{\fs36}and my dinner, which was invitation only.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.69,0:29:00.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你需要我把奶油壶递给你吗 医生\N{\fs36}Would you like me to pass you the creamer, Doc?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.78,0:29:02.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 谢谢\N{\fs36}Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.65,0:29:05.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你有毛病吗  - 你才有毛病吧\N{\fs36}- What is wrong with you? - What is wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.74,0:29:08.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你伤了我的心 今晚对我来说很重要\N{\fs36}You hurt my feelings! This night was important to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.83,0:29:11.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么伤你心了\N{\fs36}How did I hurt your feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.91,0:29:14.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的天\N{\fs36}Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.08,0:29:16.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我写了这么好的剧\N{\fs36}I wrote a hit play!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.42,0:29:22.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我爱上你了\N{\fs36}And I'm in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.52,0:29:33.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这再加一点\N{\fs36}Put that a little bit there.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.20,0:29:54.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨\N{\fs36}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.62,0:29:56.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚才是躲在那儿吗\N{\fs36}Were you hiding over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.83,0:29:59.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想打断课堂\N{\fs36}Uh, I didn't want to disrupt class.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.85,0:30:03.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这儿画的是什么\N{\fs36}What's that you're painting?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.65,0:30:06.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是 一只水母\N{\fs36}That's a - a jellyfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.37,0:30:09.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能为你做什么 Blume先生\N{\fs36}What can I do for you, Mr. Blume?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.96,0:30:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Max想跟你谈谈\N{\fs36}Max wants to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.25,0:30:13.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谈什么\N{\fs36}What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.93,0:30:15.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他想道歉吧 应该\N{\fs36}To apologize, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.64,0:30:17.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到这边聊吧\N{\fs36}Should we talk over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.70,0:30:22.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 他派你来的吗  - 是的\N{\fs36}- He sent you? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.37,0:30:25.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是他的信使吗\N{\fs36}Are you his messenger?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.34,0:30:28.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我是他朋友\N{\fs36}No, I'm his friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.24,0:30:33.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是对的 我不应该让他喝酒的\N{\fs36}You were right. I should not have allowed him to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.68,0:30:38.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得我不应该再见Max了\N{\fs36}I don't think I should see Max anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.20,0:30:41.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一定不想听到这个消息\N{\fs36}Well, he's not gonna like the sound of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.63,0:30:44.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不想 我知道 但\N{\fs36}No. No, I know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.42,0:30:47.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得他太依赖我了\N{\fs36}I think I let him get too attached.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.32,0:30:50.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得呢\N{\fs36}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.16,0:30:53.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得你已经尽力做好了\N{\fs36}Well, I think you did your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.29,0:30:59.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转告他我很抱歉\N{\fs36}Tell him I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.93,0:31:06.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs36}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.06,0:31:11.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的名字是\N{\fs36}What is your first name?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.52,0:31:14.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rosemary\N{\fs36}Rosemary.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.45,0:31:16.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的呢\N{\fs36}What's yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.45,0:31:18.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Herman\N{\fs36}Herman.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.21,0:31:25.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他给你写了封信\N{\fs36}He wrote you a letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.09,0:31:26.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的Cross小姐\N{\fs36}Dear Miss Cross...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.80,0:31:29.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想借此机会 正式向你\N{\fs36}I would like to take this opportunity to formally apologize...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.42,0:31:31.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为二十三号晚上的事情道歉\N{\fs36}for the events of the night of the 23rd.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.97,0:31:34.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不习惯喝酒\N{\fs36}I'm not accustomed to drinking alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.68,0:31:36.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有时间的话\N{\fs36}Please do me the service of coming
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.39,0:31:38.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你出席我新负责的项目的开幕式\N{\fs36}to the unveiling of a new venture I've undertaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.13,0:31:41.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你能到场\N{\fs36}I hope you will attend, if possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.10,0:31:45.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是你的朋友 Max Fisher\N{\fs36}I remain your friend, Max Fischer.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.66,0:31:54.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停止音乐 也别拍照了\N{\fs36}Cut the music, and no more pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.92,0:31:57.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 几点了 Alan  - 一点十五分\N{\fs36}- What time is it, Alan? - 1:15.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.26,0:31:59.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借过一下 先生 把薯片放下 Buchan\N{\fs36}Excuse me, gentlemen. Hey, lay off the chips, Buchan.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.84,0:32:01.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有看到她吗\N{\fs36}Did you see her?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.05,0:32:04.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 她没来这  - 去她的教室看看\N{\fs36}- She's not here. - Well, go check her classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.16,0:32:05.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要继续锯掉这些树吗\N{\fs36}Shall I go ahead and take care of this tree?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.58,0:32:08.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 稍等几分钟  - 这里在干嘛 Maxie\N{\fs36}- Let's wait a few minutes. - What's going on here, Maxie?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.06,0:32:09.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 Beck教练 很高兴见到你\N{\fs36}Oh, hey, Coach Beck. Good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.65,0:32:11.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要在这建一个新的水族馆\N{\fs36}This is where we're putting in the new aquarium.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.38,0:32:13.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在是委员会的负责人 如果你相信的话\N{\fs36}I'm in charge of the committee, if you can believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.42,0:32:15.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是我的棒球场\N{\fs36}This is my baseball diamond.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.35,0:32:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道 我相信很快它就会被移远一点的了\N{\fs36}Yeah, I know, and I believe it's being relocated a few feet over.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.18,0:32:22.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水族馆里真的会有食人鱼吗\N{\fs36}Is it true the aquarium will have piranhas?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.02,0:32:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你从哪听来的\N{\fs36}Where did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.07,0:32:26.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的线人暗示了这个可能性\N{\fs36}My source indicated that it was a possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.77,0:32:29.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的 不过食人鱼是一种很狡猾的生物\N{\fs36}Yes, it's true, but piranhas are a very tricky species.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.36,0:32:30.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Max\N{\fs36}Max?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.99,0:32:32.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 George\N{\fs36}Excuse me, George.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.70,0:32:34.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 坏消息  - 是什么\N{\fs36}- Bad news. - What's the story?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.36,0:32:36.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 她今天找人代课了  - 为什么\N{\fs36}- She had a substitute teacher today. - Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.70,0:32:38.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 可能她生病了吧  - 她肯定没有生病\N{\fs36}- I guess she got sick. - You know she's not sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.99,0:32:40.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把电话给我\N{\fs36}Give me the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.33,0:32:46.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Janet 我是Max Fisher Blume先生在吗\N{\fs36}Janet. Max Fischer. Is Mr. Blume there?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.96,0:32:49.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在哪\N{\fs36}Well, where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.34,0:32:52.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死的 他应该到这的\N{\fs36}Goddamn it. He's supposed to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.47,0:32:54.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不关心那些梭鱼\N{\fs36}I don't give a shit about the barracudas...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.93,0:32:57.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我就他妈要它建起来\N{\fs36}but fuck it, I'm building it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.47,0:33:01.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Max\N{\fs36}Max!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.10,0:33:03.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些该死的电锯是哪来的\N{\fs36}Where are those damn chain saws coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.10,0:33:05.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 他在那  - Max Max\N{\fs36}- He's right over there! - Max! Max!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.19,0:33:06.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 Guggenheim博士\N{\fs36}Oh, hello, Dr. Guggenheim.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.86,0:33:08.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你他妈以为你在干嘛\N{\fs36}What the hell do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.65,0:33:10.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在进行一个资金募集的\N{\fs36}We're having a fund-raiser for the - -
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.10,0:33:12.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把那鬼东西关掉\N{\fs36}Turn that damn thing off!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.11,0:33:13.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我这不是真的\N{\fs36}Tell me this isn't happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.99,0:33:15.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Guggenheim博士\N{\fs36}Dr. Guggenheim, I'd rather
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.12,0:33:17.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不太想在我的团队面前谈这事\N{\fs36}not have this conversation in front of my crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.85,0:33:42.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第七章\N{\fs36}...chapter seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.27,0:33:48.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一件事 今天有位新同学加入我们\N{\fs36}One more thing. We have a new student with us today.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.11,0:33:50.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他叫Max Fischer\N{\fs36}His name's Max Fischer...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.36,0:33:53.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在想跟大家说几句话\N{\fs36}and he's actually asked to say a few words to the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.11,0:33:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Max 你想到台上来讲吗\N{\fs36}Max, do you want to take it away?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.32,0:33:58.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 谢谢\N{\fs36}Sure. Thanks very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.28,0:34:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是想介绍一下自己\N{\fs36}I just wanted to introduce myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.22,0:34:10.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫Max Fischer\N{\fs36}I'm Max Fischer.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.28,0:34:13.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前就读于拉什莫尔学院\N{\fs36}I'm a former student of Rushmore Academy...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.89,0:34:15.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近被开除了\N{\fs36}which I recently got expelled from.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.74,0:34:20.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我第一次在公立学校上课\N{\fs36}This is my first time in a public school.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.22,0:34:22.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们可能会觉得\N{\fs36}I know you probably think
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.22,0:34:24.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是含着金钥匙出生的\N{\fs36}I was born with a silver spoon in my mouth...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.85,0:34:26.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我并不是什么富家子弟\N{\fs36}but I'm no elitist.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.10,0:34:29.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得这里有很多不错的设施\N{\fs36}I think you've got some great facilities...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.50,0:34:30.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很希望\N{\fs36}and I'm really looking forward
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.49,0:34:32.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能充实地在格罗弗克利夫兰学习\N{\fs36}to making the best of it here at Grover Cleveland.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.62,0:34:34.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,补充一句\N{\fs36}One footnote.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.32,0:34:36.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我注意到你们这儿没有成立击剑队\N{\fs36}I notice you don't have a fencing team.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.01,0:34:40.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会尽我所能给你们创办一个\N{\fs36}Well, I'm gonna try my hardest to start one up for you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.32,0:34:48.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Max  - 什么\N{\fs36}- Max? - Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.33,0:34:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我是Margaret Yang 我是Whitney老师班上的\N{\fs36}I. I'm Margaret Yang. I'm in Mrs. Whitney's class.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.29,0:34:53.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想告诉你我很喜欢你的发言\N{\fs36}I just wanted to tell you that I liked your speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.84,0:34:55.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs36}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.09,0:34:55.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从来没听说过\N{\fs36}I don't think I've ever heard
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.74,0:34:58.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人会主动要求在班里演讲的\N{\fs36}of anyone asking to give a speech in class before.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.80,0:35:01.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有吗 真可惜\N{\fs36}No? How unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.18,0:35:04.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有钱人的标签可能会让某些人觉得不爽\N{\fs36}The silver spoon remark might rub some people the wrong way.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.35,0:35:06.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 但我觉得我  - 什么意思 \N{\fs36}- But I think I know - - What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.27,0:35:07.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 就是  - 你知道吗\N{\fs36}- Well - - You know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.02,0:35:11.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去上课了 晚点再聊吧 Chang小姐\N{\fs36}I gotta go into class in here. I'll see you later, Ms. Chang.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.23,0:35:17.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预备\N{\fs36}En garde!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.45,0:35:28.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Janet 我是Max Fischer 他在吗\N{\fs36}Janet. Max Fischer. Is he in?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.38,0:35:34.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs36}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.71,0:35:36.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs36}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.59,0:35:39.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 嗨 Max 最近怎么样  - 很糟糕\N{\fs36}- Hey, Max, how's it going? - Terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.63,0:35:41.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我 你那天去跟Cross小姐聊的时候\N{\fs36}Tell me something. When you talked to Miss Cross the other day -
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.84,0:35:44.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有通话许可吗 抱歉\N{\fs36}Do you have a telephone pass? Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.06,0:35:47.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你有通话许可吗  - 等一下\N{\fs36}- Do you have a telephone pass? - One second.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.14,0:35:49.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须跟你说 我不知道你看上她什么了\N{\fs36}I gotta tell ya, I don't know what you see in her.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.56,0:35:51.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我觉得她不适合你\N{\fs36}I-I don't think she's right for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.35,0:35:52.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这话是什么意思\N{\fs36}What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.56,0:35:56.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的意思是 她也没多漂亮\N{\fs36}I mean, she's not that beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.98,0:36:01.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是很迷人\N{\fs36}She's not that intriguing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.24,0:36:03.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就 她身上有些特质\N{\fs36}I mean, she has something
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.22,0:36:04.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是很难琢磨的 但\N{\fs36}that you can't put your finger on, but -
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.74,0:36:06.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着 Blume先生 你的评价很宝贵\N{\fs36}Look, Mr. Blume, your comments are valuable,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.68,0:36:07.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们直接说重点吧\N{\fs36}but let's get to the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.95,0:36:10.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 孩子  - 她会再见我吗 会还是不会  \N{\fs36}- Son? - Will she see me again, yes or no?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.25,0:36:13.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 不会  - 等等\N{\fs36}- No. - Hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.54,0:36:16.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在讲电话\N{\fs36}I'm talking on the telephone.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.30,0:36:20.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托 这样也太没礼貌了\N{\fs36}Oh, come on. That's rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.82,0:36:38.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 Fischer\N{\fs36}Hey, Fischer.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.57,0:36:41.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最好滚开 小鬼\N{\fs36}You better beat it, sonny.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.44,0:36:44.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fischer 其实我一直有关注你\N{\fs36}You know, Fischer, I've been watching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.62,0:36:48.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱卖弄 说个不停\N{\fs36}Showboat. Always talkin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.16,0:36:50.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他妈妈长得不错就挑了个像Dirk那样的小子\N{\fs36}Picking a kid like Dirk because his mother's a great piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.58,0:36:52.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是一点便宜也没占到\N{\fs36}and then getting nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.62,0:36:54.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像你做的任何事\N{\fs36}Like everything you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.71,0:36:56.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盛大演出 毫无水花\N{\fs36}Big show. No results.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.96,0:37:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得在Calloway夫人的\N{\fs36}What do you call getting a hand job from
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.00,0:37:01.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捷豹后座手淫算什么\N{\fs36}Mrs. Calloway in the back of her Jaguar?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.01,0:37:04.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个扯淡的谎话\N{\fs36}A fucking lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.76,0:37:07.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为我退学是因为水族馆的事吗\N{\fs36}You think I got kicked out for just the aquarium?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.64,0:37:11.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是因为手淫的事\N{\fs36}Nah. It was the hand job.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.52,0:37:14.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再告诉你一点 爽翻了\N{\fs36}You want to know something else? It was worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.61,0:37:20.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 让你在上次晚餐里那么尴尬\N{\fs36}I'm sorry I embarrassed you at dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.53,0:37:23.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也请帮我转告那谁 我很抱歉\N{\fs36}And please apologize to what's-his-name for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.32,0:37:25.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会的\N{\fs36}I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.74,0:37:28.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吗\N{\fs36}You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.41,0:37:30.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺好的 但是很想念拉什莫尔\N{\fs36}Yeah, I'm fine, but I miss Rushmore.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.16,0:37:34.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想念这里的季节变换\N{\fs36}I miss the seasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.79,0:37:37.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着树叶由黄变绿\N{\fs36}Watching the leaves change.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.17,0:37:39.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺便问问 图书馆什么时候关\N{\fs36}By the way, what time does the library close?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.42,0:37:42.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有本过期的书要还\N{\fs36}I've got an overdue book to turn in.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.18,0:37:52.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你的笔迹 对吧\N{\fs36}That is your handwriting, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.92,0:37:55.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这本书是我十三岁那年\N{\fs36}My husband gave me this book...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.08,0:37:57.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我丈夫来英国的时候给我的\N{\fs36}when he came to visit England when I was 13.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.57,0:37:58.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后他去了拉什莫尔\N{\fs36}And he went to Rushmore,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.61,0:38:01.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他去世以后 我就把它捐给图书馆了\N{\fs36}so when he died I gave it to the library here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.03,0:38:05.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你总让我想起他 你知道吗\N{\fs36}You remind me of him, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.36,0:38:08.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吗\N{\fs36}I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.58,0:38:10.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会\N{\fs36}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.37,0:38:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fs36}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.57,0:38:17.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是拉什莫尔养蜂社的成员 是不是\N{\fs36}you were a member of the Rushmore Beekeepers, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.42,0:38:20.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 我是社长\N{\fs36}Yeah. I was president of them.
