Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.89,1:04:57.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道\N{\fs36}You know, uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.47,1:05:00.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是很可爱 但是她太混乱了\N{\fs36}she's sweet, but she's fucked-up.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.81,1:05:06.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见 孩子\N{\fs36}Adios, muchacho.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.48,1:05:08.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你还好吧\N{\fs36}Hey, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.90,1:05:12.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 这几天我是有点孤单\N{\fs36}Mmm. I'm a little bit lonely these days.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.69,1:05:47.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Max\N{\fs36}Max?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.36,1:05:49.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这儿做什么\N{\fs36}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.78,1:05:54.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道 上帝啊 那群人不知道从哪儿来的\N{\fs36}I don't know. Jesus. They came at me out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.36,1:05:56.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 突然冲过来了  - 什么\N{\fs36}- It was so sudden. - What?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.16,1:06:00.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我可以用一下你的电话吗 我刚被车撞了\N{\fs36}I'm sorry. Can I use your phone? I just got hit by a car.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.86,1:06:03.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦天呐 你你你还好吗\N{\fs36}Oh, my God. A-A-Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.40,1:06:05.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说啥\N{\fs36}Hmm? What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.21,1:06:07.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 快进来  - 谢谢\N{\fs36}- Come inside. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.82,1:06:11.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去给你拿点药\N{\fs36}I'm gonna get something for your head.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.76,1:06:21.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 这就是一切发生的地方\N{\fs36}So, this is where it all happens.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.77,1:06:24.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 一切什么事发生  - 我不知道\N{\fs36}- All what happens? - I wouldn't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.82,1:06:26.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说你为什么甩了Blume\N{\fs36}So, why did you dump Blume?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.14,1:06:29.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你无关\N{\fs36}That's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.48,1:06:32.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道和我无关\N{\fs36}I know it's not.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.88,1:06:35.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我刚被车撞了 现在脑子有点乱\N{\fs36}But I just got hit by a car, and I'm a little confused right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.88,1:06:38.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为你为Blume而甩了我 然后我又听说\N{\fs36}I mean, I thought you dumped me for Blume. Then I hear
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.20,1:06:40.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没甩你 因为我们从来没交往过\N{\fs36}I never dumped you because we were never going out.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.98,1:06:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你和我聊会天的话就再好不过了\N{\fs36}It would just help me if you talked to me for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.00,1:06:45.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我发生了什么\N{\fs36}Tell me what happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.08,1:06:50.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs36}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.42,1:06:56.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先 他已婚\N{\fs36}A, he's married.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.09,1:07:01.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其次 他讨厌自己\N{\fs36}B, he hates himself.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.18,1:07:02.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有第三点\N{\fs36}And C, Well...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.06,1:07:06.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他撞坏了你的自行车 对吧\N{\fs36}he smashed up your bicycle, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.14,1:07:08.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前的自行车 是的\N{\fs36}My previous bicycle, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.18,1:07:11.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么样的人能做出那样的事啊\N{\fs36}Well, what sort of a person does something like that?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.98,1:07:13.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fs36}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.86,1:07:19.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战争对男人有奇怪的影响\N{\fs36}War does funny things to men.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.92,1:07:23.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他以为你甩了他是因为Edward Appleby\N{\fs36}He thinks you dumped him because of Edward Appleby.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.06,1:07:27.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么意思\N{\fs36}What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.68,1:07:31.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意思就是 你住在他住过的房间里\N{\fs36}Well, I mean, you live in his room...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.92,1:07:35.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四周都是他用过的东西 感觉有点\N{\fs36}with all his stuff. It's kind of
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.51,1:07:38.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和他结过婚\N{\fs36}I was married to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.40,1:07:41.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fs36}I know you were.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.55,1:07:47.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 我还是要说Edward一个指甲里的\N{\fs36}Although, I will say that Edward has more spark and character...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.24,1:07:50.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪光点 特质和想象力\N{\fs36}and imagination in one fingernail...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.35,1:07:53.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就比Herman Blume整个人的还多\N{\fs36}than Herman Blume has in his entire body.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.56,1:07:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个死去的指甲\N{\fs36}One dead fingernail.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.00,1:08:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs36}Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.00,1:08:05.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个死去的指甲\N{\fs36}One dead fingernail.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.46,1:08:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺便问一下 他怎么死的\N{\fs36}How did he die, by the way?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.74,1:08:15.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溺水\N{\fs36}He drowned.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.10,1:08:18.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你母亲怎么死的\N{\fs36}How did your mother die?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.66,1:08:21.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,癌症\N{\fs36}She got cancer.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.02,1:08:28.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍住别动 好吗\N{\fs36}Hold still for a moment, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.78,1:08:37.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很美\N{\fs36}You're very pretty.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.54,1:08:40.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs36}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.59,1:09:04.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是假的血吗\N{\fs36}Is this fake blood?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.06,1:09:10.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs36}Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.77,1:09:14.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和Herman真是天生一对\N{\fs36}You know, you and Herman deserve each other.
