Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.22,1:11:20.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么没有\N{\fs36}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.44,1:11:21.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那是假的\N{\fs36}Because it was a fake.
