Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.08,1:11:43.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 Margaret\N{\fs36}I'm sorry, Margaret.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.52,1:11:48.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎样 很高兴见到你\N{\fs36}Well, anyway, nice to see you.
