Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.33,1:25:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 还告诉我要戴领带\N{\fs36}Yeah, and he told me to wear a tie.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.24,1:25:35.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 祝贺你啊 Max  - 谢谢 Yang太太\N{\fs36}- Congratulations, Max. - Thank you very much, Mrs. Yang.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.79,1:25:39.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实两年前我写过另一个版本\N{\fs36}I, uh, actually wrote a different version of the play two years ago...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.05,1:25:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在拉什莫尔的时候没法演出\N{\fs36}but I couldn't get it done over at Rushmore.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.09,1:25:44.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 哦真的吗 为什么  - 太政治化吗\N{\fs36}- Oh, really? Why? - Too political?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.34,1:25:47.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 一个小孩在排练的时候被炸飞了手指\N{\fs36}No, a kid got his finger blown off during rehearsals.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.47,1:25:50.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好啊 Fischer一家 你们好\N{\fs36}A very good evening to you, Fischers. Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.22,1:25:52.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cross小姐 我想向你介绍我的父亲 Bert Fischer\N{\fs36}Miss Cross, I'd like for you to meet my father, Bert Fischer.
