Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.27,1:25:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我朋友 Rosemary Cross\N{\fs36}This is my friend, Rosemary Cross.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.24,1:25:59.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你好 Rosemary  - 终于见到您了很高兴 Bert\N{\fs36}- Hello, Rosemary. - Nice to meet you at last, Bert.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.36,1:26:00.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Blume先生你认识的\N{\fs36}Of course you know Mr. Blume.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.94,1:26:04.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想向大家介绍Yang先生和Yang太太\N{\fs36}I'd also like everyone to meet Mr. And Mrs. Yang.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.12,1:26:06.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 这是Margaret  - 你好 Margaret\N{\fs36}- This is Margaret. - Hello, Margaret.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.28,1:26:08.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很高兴见到你 Cross小姐\N{\fs36}It's nice to meet you, Miss Cross.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.20,1:26:10.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很惊讶他们真的让他在舞台上搭了营火\N{\fs36}I'm surprised they let him build a real campfire on the stage.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.64,1:26:12.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明显是个安全隐患啊\N{\fs36}It's clearly a safety hazard.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.28,1:26:14.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去年他还想养食人鱼呢\N{\fs36}Well, last year he tried to raise piranhas.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.20,1:26:15.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道\N{\fs36}Yeah, I know he did.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.00,1:26:17.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得如何 Littlejeans先生\N{\fs36}What did you think, Mr. Littlejeans?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.50,1:26:19.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有史以来最棒的剧\N{\fs36}Best play ever, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.59,1:26:23.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为这是一场很真实的表演\N{\fs36}I thought it was a very realistic performance.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.67,1:26:26.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是么 Fischer打断了我一半的台词\N{\fs36}Yeah? Fischer stepped over half my bloody lines.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.80,1:26:28.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点意思 我都没注意\N{\fs36}That's funny. I didn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.80,1:26:31.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Blume先生 Ronny和Donny觉得军校怎么样\N{\fs36}Mr. Blume, how are Ronny and Donny enjoying military school?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.44,1:26:32.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们很喜欢\N{\fs36}They love it.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.28,1:26:34.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸运的混蛋\N{\fs36}Lucky bastards.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.78,1:26:37.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜你是个神经外科医生\N{\fs36}I understand you're a neurosurgeon.
