Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.82,1:26:48.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你今晚真棒 Margaret\N{\fs36}You were incredible tonight, Margaret.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.04,1:26:51.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你就是那个可怜的女孩  - 谢谢\N{\fs36}- You were that poor girl. - Thank you.
